==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cancellate
<hw>Can"cel*late</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>cancellatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>cancellare</ets>, See
<er>Cancel</er>, <pos>v. t.</pos>]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Consisting of a network of veins, without intermediate parenchyma,
as the leaves of certain plants; latticelike.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Having the surface covered with
raised lines, crossing at right angles.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cancellated</ent>⟦br⟧
